 Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="18" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Under the residence te</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">st, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Mwahasi</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> would not be entitled to </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">legal aid</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> to challenge the UKBA’s refusal of her application for the DDV Concession</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, even though it raises a matter of public importance</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The case al</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">so highlights the difficulties she had in obtaining exceptional case f</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">unding from the Legal Aid Agency</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. Although th</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">is decision also </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">appears to be misguided.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span></li></ol><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="19" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li styl